description.en: This ontology introduces the definition of a set of bicycle parking facilities related terms. It reuses and extends the MobiVoc (see http://schema.mobivoc.org/) and the schema.org (see https://schema.org) vocabularies.

comment.en: Real-time capacity of a civic structure.
Specifies a location feature by providing a structured value representing a feature of an accommodation as a property-value pair of varying degrees of formality.

An instance of this class represents the legal agent making (or seeking) a particular offering. This can be a legal body or a person. A business entity has at least a primary mailing address and contact details. For this, typical address standards (vCard) and location data (geo, WGS84) can be attached. Note that the location of the business entity is not necessarily the location from which the product or service is being available.

comment.de: Lagerung im speziell gestalteten Raum eines Gebäudes, nur für Anwohner zugänglich.
comment.en: Bicycle parking in the specifically designed space of a building, only accessible to local residents.
comment.fr: Stockage dans l'espace spécialement conçu d'un bâtiment, accessible uniquement aux résidents locaux.
comment.nl: Stalling in specifiek daarvoor ingerichte ruimte van een gebouw, enkel toegankelijk voor omwonenden uit de buurt.

comment.de: Überdachter und abschließbarer Fahrradabstellplatz auf öffentlichen Straßen.
comment.en: Covered and lockable bicycle parking facility on public roads.
comment.fr: Parking vélo couvert et verrouillable sur la voie publique.
comment.nl: Overdekte en afsluitbare fietsenstalling op openbare wegen.

comment.en: Bicycle parking facility available for public use.
comment.fr: Stationnement pour vélos disponible pour un usage public.

comment.de: Gerät, an dem Fahrräder zum Parken sicher befestigt werden können.
comment.en: Device to which bicycles can be securely attached for parking purposes.
comment.fr: Dispositif auquel des bicyclettes peuvent être solidement attachées à des fins de stationnement.
comment.nl: Apparaat waaraan fietsen veilig kunnen worden bevestigd voor parkeren.

comment.en: Building or structure designed for use as a bicycle parking facility.

comment.de: Eine Parkfunktion, die anzeigt, dass eine Fahrradpumpe verfügbar ist.
comment.en: A parking facility feature that indicates it has a bicycle pump available.
comment.fr: Une fonctionnalité de parking indiquant qu’une pompe à vélo est disponible.
comment.nl: Een parkeerfaciliteit die aangeeft dat er een fietspomp beschikbaar is.

comment.de: Eine Parkfunktion, die anzeigt, dass ein Fahrradwartungsservice verfügbar ist.
comment.en: A parking facility feature that indicates it has a bicycle maintenance service available.
comment.fr: Une fonctionnalité de parking indiquant qu’un service d’entretien des vélos est disponible.
comment.nl: Een parkeerfaciliteit die aangeeft dat er een fietsonderhoudsdienst beschikbaar is.

comment.de: Eine Parkfunktion, die anzeigt, dass eine Ladestation für Elektrofahrräder verfügbar ist.
comment.en: A parking facility feature that indicates it has an electrical bicycle charging point available.
comment.fr: Une fonction de parcage indiquant qu’il dispose d’un point de charge pour vélo électrique.
comment.nl: Een parkeervoorziening die aangeeft dat er een elektrisch fietslaadpunt beschikbaar is.

comment.de: Eine Parkmöglichkeit, die anzeigt, dass ein Fahrradverleih zur Verfügung steht.
comment.en: A parking facility feature that indicates it has a bicycle rental service available.
comment.fr: Un parking qui indique qu’un service de location de vélos est disponible.
comment.nl: Een parkeerfaciliteit die aangeeft dat er een fietsverhuur beschikbaar is.

comment.de: Ein Service, bei dem Fahrräder für Einzelpersonen kurzfristig zur gemeinsamen Nutzung zur Verfügung gestellt werden.
comment.en: A service in which bicycles are made available for shared use to individuals on a short term basis.
comment.fr: Un service dans lequel des vélos sont mis à la disposition des particuliers pour une utilisation partagée à court terme.
comment.nl: Een service waarbij fietsen op korte termijn beschikbaar worden gesteld voor gedeeld gebruik aan particulieren.

comment.de: Eine Parkmöglichkeit, die anzeigt, dass ein Toilettenservice verfügbar ist.
comment.en: A parking facility feature that indicates it has a toilet service available.
comment.fr: Une fonctionnalité de parking qui indique qu'il a un service de toilette disponible.
comment.nl: Een parkeerfaciliteit die aangeeft dat er een toiletservice beschikbaar is.

comment.en: A feature available for a given parking facility.
The mailing address.
A WebSite is a set of related web pages and other items typically served from a single web domain and accessible via URLs.
The geographic coordinates of a place or event.
A structured value representing a price or price range for an item.
Any facility or area assigned for parking vehicles. A parking facility can provide one or more parking spaces.
A public structure, such as a town hall or concert hall, parking facility or charging point.
The geographic shape of a place. A GeoShape can be described using several properties whose values are based on latitude/longitude pairs.

comment.de: Eine Funktion, die anzeigt, dass Überwachungskameras verfügbar sind.
comment.en: A facility feature that indicates it has surveillance cameras available.
comment.fr: Une fonctionnalité qui indique que des caméras de surveillance sont disponibles.
comment.nl: Een faciliteitsfunctie die aangeeft dat er bewakingscamera's beschikbaar zijn.

comment.de: Eine Einrichtungsfunktion, die angibt, dass ein Schließfachdienst verfügbar ist.
comment.en: A facility feature that indicates it has a locker service available.
comment.fr: Une fonctionnalité qui indique qu’un service de casier est disponible.
comment.nl: Een faciliteitsfunctie die aangeeft dat er een lockerservice beschikbaar is.

comment.de: Eine Einrichtungsfunktion, die angibt, dass eine Personalüberwachung verfügbar ist.
comment.en: A facility feature that indicates it has personnel supervision available.
comment.fr: Une fonctionnalité qui indique qu’une supervision du personnel est disponible.
comment.nl: Een faciliteitsfunctie die aangeeft dat er personeelsbewaking beschikbaar is.

comment.de: Ein Funktionsmerkmal, das angibt, dass es über ein elektronisches Zugangssystem verfügt.
comment.en: A facility feature that indicates it has an electronic access system.
comment.fr: Une fonctionnalité qui indique qu’il dispose d’un système d’accès électronique.
comment.nl: Een faciliteitsfunctie die aangeeft dat het een elektronisch toegangssysteem heeft.

comment.en: A security feature available for a given location or facility.
A vehicle is a device that is designed or used to transport people or cargo over land, water, air, or through space.
Entities that have a somewhat fixed, physical extension.
A contact point for customer service.
A photograph.

comment.undefined: A bicycle that is allowed in a given parking facility.

comment.en: The day of the week, e.g. used to specify to which day the opening hours of an OpeningHoursSpecification refer.
A map.
Specific time a price specification is due for.
Exit of a parking facility where vehicles can leave.

comment.de: Ein Fahrrad, das von mehr als einer Person gefahren werden kann.
comment.en: A bicycle designed to be ridden by more than one person.
comment.fr: Un vélo conçu pour être monté par plus d'une personne.
comment.nl: Een fiets die ontworpen is om door meer dan één persoon te worden bereden.

comment.de: Ein normales Fahrrad, das keine Besonderheiten aufweist.
comment.en: A regular bicycle that does not have any special features.
comment.fr: Un vélo ordinaire qui ne présente aucune particularité.
comment.nl: Een gewone fiets die geen speciale functies heeft.

comment.de: Ein Fahrrad, das speziell für den Transport von Lasten ausgelegt ist.
comment.en: A bicycle specially adapted to transport load.
comment.fr: Un vélo spécialement adapté au transport de charge.
comment.nl: Een speciaal aangepaste fiets om lading te vervoeren.

comment.en: An electrically powered bicycle.
A single-track vehicle, having two wheels attached to a frame, one behind the other.
Capacity of a civic structure.
A structured value providing information about the opening hours of a place or a certain service inside a place.
Entrance of a parking facility where vehicles can enter.

comment.undefined: Indicates the time unit a value is specified for.

comment.en: Relates the civic structure to its capacity.
Place close to another place.
The day of the week for which certain opening hours are valid.
The date of the given real-time capacity.
The owner of a civic structure or facility. Owner and operator can be different business entities.
Description of how parking facility users must proceed when their bicycles are removed.
Indicates if a facility is temporarily closed due to works, events, maintenance, etc.
Indicates extra information about the opening hours of the facility. E.g. Closed on holidays.
Indicates that the usage of the civic structure is for free.
A language someone may use with or at the item, service or place. Please use one of the language codes from the IETF BCP 47 standard.

comment.undefined: Indicates the total number of parking spaces of a parking facility.

comment.en: The currency of the price. Use standard formats: ISO 4217 currency format (e.g. USD).
The operator of a civic structure or facility. Operator and owner can be different business entitites.
The offer price of a product, or of a price component when attached to PriceSpecification and its subtypes.
The closing hour of the place or service on the given day(s) of the week.
Indicates that a price specification is due for a certain time specification.
An amenity feature (e.g. a characteristic or service) of a place or accomodation.
Email address.
A contact point for a person or organization.
The hours during which a service or contact is available.
Indicates the current value of the real-time capacity.
A telephone number.
A URL to a map of the place.
Indicates the specific type of bicycle that is allowed in a certain parking facility.
The initial opening date of a parking facility (in ISO 8601 date format).
A photograph of this place.

comment.undefined: Describes the exit of a parking facility.

comment.en: The WebSite or SoftwareApplication where the interactions took place.
Physical address of the item.
The final closing date of a parking facility (in ISO 8601 date format).
Indicates the maximum amount of time that bicycles are allowed to be parked in a certain parking facility.
The opening hour of the place or service on the given day(s) of the week.

comment.undefined: Indicates the start value of a time period.

comment.en: Indicates the operational restrictions that a certain parking facility may have.
Indicates if a facility is sheltered or has any type of roof covering.
Indicates a type of bicycle that is allowed in a certain parking facility.
One or more detailed price specifications, indicating the unit price and delivery or payment charges.

A person or organization can have different contact points, for different purposes. For example, a sales contact point, a PR contact point and so on. This property is used to specify the kind of contact point.
Indicates the type of audience that can make use of a certain parking facility.
The geo coordinates of a place.
A flag to signal that a Place is open to public visitors.
An unambiguous reference to the resource within a given context.
The name of an item.
The owner of the data about a certain bicycle parking facility.
Indicates the total number of levels a parking facility has.
Description of the conditions under which a bicycle may be removed from a certain parking facility.

comment.undefined: Indicates the end value of a time period.

comment.en: Describes the entrance of a parking facility.
Indicates whether a certain type of allowed bicycle has a counting system or not, for a given parking facility.
Indicates the maximum amount of bicycle of a certain type that are allowed in a parking facility.
The hours during which a service or contact is available.

comment.undefined: Indicates that a time period overnight is possible.
